data.description: Beautifal home in a country setting on 2 acres! Master suite has large walk in closet with tall windows. Master bath has garden tub, double vanity, separate show, walkin closets and beautifal tile floors; bonus room and large bonus/4th bedroom upstairs; large eat in kitchen with tile floors and movable island; 18x12 hobby room/laundry room recently added. Cabinet and TV box in living room; real hardwood floors in living room, dining room and hallway;2 car garage. Inground salt water pool by Alewine with new liner. Large storage shed;  Horses are allowed. A true must see!
